rComments: Very difficult marker. He is nice and explains well but dont let it fool you into thinking that you will receive a favourable grade. Participation and attendance only matters in syllabus. It has no positive impact on your marks. Only exams and paper work count towards your grade so work hard on it.
Prof Rene Bogovic is a real gem to utsc. He is just amazing and very very inspirational. I learned a lot in his classes
